{"tid":2141759,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"專家警告：疫苗恐對肥胖者失效","createTime":"2020-08-06T03:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T05:38:35.000Z","uid":285559,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3ecc49ca7506efa4517dea66baea8bef493eb538","tid":2141759,"uid":285559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:00:54.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）肆虐全球，各國無不期盼疫苗問世，然而醫界卻提醒，若民眾過胖可能導致疫苗效果降低，甚至無效。<br />\n<br />\n根據《CNN》報導，在武漢肺炎影響下，美國有460萬人受感染，逾15萬人死亡，不少民眾面對此危機，紛紛將疫苗視為救命稻草，對此，美國醫界警告，過去的經驗顯示，各類疫苗對肥胖人士的保護力不如普通人，「沒有理由相信武漢肺炎疫苗會有所不同」。<br />\n<br />\n美國北卡羅來納大學營養學副教授謝赫（Raz Shaikh）表示，民眾過去常施打的流感、B肝、破傷風及狂犬病等疫苗，在肥胖人士體內作用的效果比普通人群來得低，使其更容易感染和患病。<br />\n<br />\n謝赫進一步設問道，「明年我們會有專門爲肥胖者量身定制Covid疫苗嗎」、「疫苗在肥胖者中仍然有用嗎」，「我們的預測是否定的」。<br />\n<br />\n按美國疾病防治中心（CDC）今年公布的數據，每10名美國成年人中就有4名肥胖，其中嚴重肥胖的比率更高達1成，使該國成為全球肥胖人口比例最高的國家之一。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2020/08/05/health/obesity-covid-vaccine-effectiveness-wellness/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2020%2F08%2F05%2Fhealth%2Fobesity-covid-vaccine-effectiveness-wellness%2Findex.html&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F8fSVjQS2PdSygdC4qSdyAU%3D&h=6d84007f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2020%2F08%2F05%2Fhealth%2Fobesity-covid-vaccine-effectiveness-wellness%2Findex.html&h=d47f214c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2020/08/05/health/obesity-covid-vaccine-effectiveness-wellness/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://health.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3251527\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhealth.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3251527&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F8fSVjQS2PdSygdC4qSdyAU%3D&h=8831df96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhealth.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3251527&h=ac2809d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://health.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3251527</a>"},{"pid":"99000e738e760bb116906e5ff9eb7efb5b053754","tid":2141759,"uid":251872,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:02:03.000Z","msg":"嚇到我即刻減肥"},{"pid":"13a9dba38f4a990d7ce36586797af07ad3fc13da","tid":2141759,"uid":14494,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:02:21.000Z","msg":"肥撚肥閪逃唔過natural selection<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df11d166d81609e165458a272b08d31cb5a1ad21","tid":2141759,"uid":204356,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:04:39.000Z","msg":"美國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c6e250a6117093aa90b0411fafa45f055c8614","tid":2141759,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:05:25.000Z","msg":"美國仲唔仆街"},{"pid":"f4929df96371869452d6ef840b922e6b363a0cb5","tid":2141759,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:05:40.000Z","msg":"下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e9931bb13b2be894b178bbae0729f7997ae4fc","tid":2141759,"uid":300935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:06:50.000Z","msg":"stay home個個肥曬，效力大減<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b390a2dce295dfc780cac86fe49b46a702791d","tid":2141759,"uid":196552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:07:00.000Z","msg":"營養學副教授"},{"pid":"08f9865076d1c0a6c9ead8b4b7982b7e2eb0a1f1","tid":2141759,"uid":266342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:07:55.000Z","msg":"習維尼無疫苗用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ff4d7a6805e0e955494088